‎奶奶 爷爷 你们好
Hey, Grandma. Hey, Grandpa.

27
00:01:06,357 --> 00:01:09,652
‎莉亚 我的孙女
Leia. My grandbaby.

28
00:01:09,736 --> 00:01:13,281
‎嘿 孩子 你可真是长高了
Hey, kiddo.
Boy, you sure have gotten tall.

29
00:01:13,364 --> 00:01:16,826
‎而且胸花怒放了 恭喜
Oh, and congratulations.
Those buds are blooming.

30
00:01:17,660 --> 00:01:19,287
‎您…气色也不赖？
Yours… look good too?

31
00:01:20,288 --> 00:01:23,208
‎我敢说你在篮球场上肯定彪悍得很
Why, I bet you're a holy terror
on the basketball court.

32
00:01:23,291 --> 00:01:26,795
‎我听说你有你妈妈的跳投绝活
‎还有你爸爸的…姓
I hear you got your mom's jump shot
and your dad's

33
00:01:26,878 --> 00:01:27,879
‎我听说你有你妈妈的跳投绝活
‎还有你爸爸的…姓
last name.

34
00:01:29,756 --> 00:01:32,133
‎-我去下洗手间
‎-喂
-I'm gonna take a bathroom break.
-Hey, hey, hey.

35
00:01:32,717 --> 00:01:36,471
‎拧水龙头要小心 出水烫死人
Just be careful with the faucets.
The water comes out, like, scalding hot.

36
00:01:36,554 --> 00:01:39,808
‎艾瑞克 水是正常温度
It's a normal temperature, Eric.

37
00:01:40,600 --> 00:01:42,894
‎是你小子皮太嫩
You've just got that sensitive baby skin.

38
00:01:44,062 --> 00:01:45,438
‎要知道
You know,

39
00:01:45,522 --> 00:01:49,067
‎我很期待今年独立日的周末
I am so excited
about this Fourth of July weekend.

40
00:01:49,150 --> 00:01:52,570
‎大家一起烤香肠 看焰火…
We are gonna grill weenies,
watch the fireworks…

41
00:01:52,654 --> 00:01:54,405
‎我还租了《小美人鱼》
I even rented <i>The Little Mermaid</i>.

42
00:01:54,489 --> 00:01:57,200
‎谢谢妈妈 但她已经不喜欢这个了
Oh. Thanks, Mom,
but she's not really into that anymore.

43
00:01:57,283 --> 00:01:59,661
