[young woman] <i>Hello, Wisconsin!</i>

50
00:02:19,013 --> 00:02:21,891
‎谁想来块热乎乎的肉桂甜饼？
Who wants a warm snickerdoodle?

51
00:02:21,975 --> 00:02:25,353
‎我要 妈 闻头发有点诡异哈
I do. It's a little weird
that you're smelling my hair, Mom.

52
00:02:26,146 --> 00:02:30,024
‎圣诞节过后 我就没见过你了
‎所以我想怎么闻就怎么闻
I haven't seen you since Christmas,
so I will smell you however I want,

53
00:02:30,108 --> 00:02:31,860
‎你不准反抗
and you're fine with it.

54
00:02:31,943 --> 00:02:36,489
‎对了 唐娜
‎艾瑞克把你新书的评论寄给我们了
So, Donna, Eric sent us
the review of your new book.

55
00:02:36,573 --> 00:02:37,490
‎我们看了哦
We read it.

56
00:02:37,574 --> 00:02:38,825
‎你们看我新书了？
Oh, you read my book?

57
00:02:38,908 --> 00:02:40,618
‎没有 看的是书评
No, the review.

58
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:43,163
‎谢了 福婶
Thanks, Mrs. F.

59
00:02:43,246 --> 00:02:44,372
Aww…

60
00:02:44,455 --> 00:02:47,375
‎-我希望你叫“妈” 知道吗？
‎-知道
-I wish you'd call me Mom, you know?
-I know.

61
00:02:48,668 --> 00:02:49,502
‎好吧
Okay.

62
00:02:49,586 --> 00:02:50,503
‎有朝一日吧
Someday.

63
00:02:50,587 --> 00:02:51,963
‎就这周末
This weekend.

64
00:02:53,256 --> 00:02:55,466
