Going great. I'm an adjunct professor now,

66
00:02:57,927 --> 00:03:00,013
‎也就有了永久停车位
which means I got
a permanent parking space

67
00:03:00,096 --> 00:03:01,264
‎放我的自行车
for my bicycle.

68
00:03:02,432 --> 00:03:04,767
‎老爸 课程受欢迎就会这样
That's what happens
when your course is super popular, Dad.

69
00:03:04,851 --> 00:03:06,728
‎“《星球大战》的宗教”哇？
"The Religion of <i>Star Wars</i>"?

70
00:03:06,811 --> 00:03:08,188
‎是的
Oh yeah.

71
00:03:08,271 --> 00:03:10,523
‎下回打仗 这个国家输定了
This country's gonna lose the next war.

72
00:03:11,107 --> 00:03:13,902
‎如果是星际善恶争霸就不会
Not if it's an intergalactic battle
between good and evil.

73
00:03:15,028 --> 00:03:17,155
‎嘿 我去打一会篮球
Hey, I'm gonna go shoot some hoops.

74
00:03:17,238 --> 00:03:19,657
‎跟爷爷奶奶说说 咱们暑假要做什么
Hey, Leia, tell your grandparents
what we're doing this summer.

75
00:03:19,741 --> 00:03:20,575
‎我们要去…
Oh, we're going to--

76
00:03:20,658 --> 00:03:23,661
‎阿拉巴马州的亨茨维尔
‎参加父女太空营
We're going to Huntsville, Alabama,
for a little father-daughter Space Camp.

77
00:03:24,871 --> 00:03:27,498
‎就我俩…足足俩礼拜
Just the two of us… for two weeks.

78
00:03:27,582 --> 00:03:29,959
‎休斯顿 请求玩耍 完毕
[imitates radio static]
Houston, permission to have fun, over.

79
00:03:31,252 --> 00:03:33,296
‎休斯顿 能收到吗？完毕
[imitates static]
Houston, do you read me, over?

80
00:03:34,756 --> 00:03:37,175
‎-准许玩耍
‎-对啦
-[imitates static] Permission granted.
-[laughs] Yeah!

81
00:03:38,092 --> 00:03:39,636
‎但你…没有说“完毕”
But you… you didn't say "over."

82
00:03:39,719 --> 00:03:42,013
‎-妈妈
‎-好了 莉亚 去投篮吧
-Mom?
-Okay, Leia, go shoot some baskets.

83
00:03:42,096 --> 00:03:44,015
