I think she might be
at that age where she needs space.

90
00:04:03,284 --> 00:04:05,787
‎我有给她空间…太空营
I'm giving her space… camp.

91
00:04:07,789 --> 00:04:10,667
‎-太空营
‎-艾瑞克和莉亚最近有点磕绊
-Space Camp.
-Eric's having a hard time with Leia.

92
00:04:10,750 --> 00:04:12,919
‎38岁…是个坎儿
It's a tough age… 38.

93
00:04:13,002 --> 00:04:14,212
‎好吧
Okay. Okay.

94
00:04:14,295 --> 00:04:19,217
‎我只知道无论怎样
‎我都会爱她 在她身后支持她
All I know is that I'm going to love her
and stand behind her, no matter what.

95
00:04:19,300 --> 00:04:21,010
‎这主意不错
That is a great idea.

96
00:04:21,678 --> 00:04:25,348
‎因为站在他们身后 就更方便…
Because when you stand
behind your kids, it's easier--

97
00:04:25,431 --> 00:04:27,016
‎打他们屁股
[all] To put your foot in their ass.

98
00:04:27,100 --> 00:04:28,393
‎明白 老爸 谢了
We got it, Dad. Thanks.

99
00:04:28,476 --> 00:04:31,396
[hip-hop beat playing]

100
00:04:34,232 --> 00:04:36,276
[young woman] ♪ <i>And I'm here ♪</i>

101
00:04:36,359 --> 00:04:38,278
<i>♪ To remind you ♪</i>

102
00:04:38,361 --> 00:04:42,198
<i>♪ Of the mess you left</i>
<i>When you went away ♪</i>

103
00:04:42,282 --> 00:04:44,242
<i>♪ It's not fair ♪</i>

104
00:04:44,325 --> 00:04:46,035
<i>♪ To deny me ♪</i>

105
00:04:46,119 --> 00:04:49,580
<i>♪ Of the cross I bear</i>
<i>That you gave to me ♪</i>

106
00:04:49,664 --> 00:04:52,667
<i>♪ You, you, you oughta know! ♪</i>

107
00:05:00,008 --> 00:05:00,967
‎你好
Hello.

108
00:05:01,843 --> 00:05:03,386
‎你在干嘛 变态？
What are you doing, creeper?

109
00:05:03,469 --> 00:05:04,762
‎没做什么怪事 我只是站在你窗外
Oh, nothing weird! [laughs]

110
00:05:04,846 --> 00:05:07,181
‎没做什么怪事 我只是站在你窗外
I was just standing outside your window
and watching you sing

111
00:05:07,265 --> 00:05:10,768
‎看着你唱歌 想象着当你是什么感觉
and wondering
what it would be like to… be you.

112
00:05:11,936 --> 00:05:13,438
‎我走了
I'll go now. [gasps]

113
00:05:13,521 --> 00:05:16,441
‎除非你想听我从芝加哥搞到的盗版带
Unless you want to hear
a cool bootleg I got in Chicago.

114
00:05:16,524 --> 00:05:17,775
‎接着说
Oh, I'm listening.

115
00:05:17,859 --> 00:05:19,485
‎嗯 可牛了
Yeah, it's, uh, pretty major.

116
00:05:20,570 --> 00:05:21,571
‎超牛的盗版
Big-time bootleg.

117
00:05:22,238 --> 00:05:24,115
‎盗版得不行
The bootiest of legs.

118
00:05:25,074 --> 00:05:25,908
‎赶紧去拿就对了
Just go get it.

119
00:05:25,992 --> 00:05:26,868
‎马上
On it.

120
00:05:27,910 --> 00:05:29,620
‎等我回来时 你一定要在啊
Please be here when I get back.

121
00:05:30,121 --> 00:05:32,498
["Sad Tomorrow" by The Muffs playing]

122
00:05:32,582 --> 00:05:36,753
‎这是你妈妈以前的房间
‎而你爸就住在隔壁？
So this was your mom's old room,
and your dad lived next door?

123
00:05:37,378 --> 00:05:39,630
‎我敢说他们经常在这里打炮
I bet they boned in here all the time.

124
00:05:40,923 --> 00:05:41,883
‎这下就明白多了
Explains a lot.

125
00:05:42,675 --> 00:05:43,760
‎有时
Sometimes,

126
00:05:43,843 --> 00:05:44,969
‎在深夜
late at night,

127
00:05:45,636 --> 00:05:47,221
‎周围一片寂静的时候
when everything's quiet,

128
00:05:48,097 --> 00:05:49,390
‎我依然能听到…
I can still hear the…

129
00:05:50,016 --> 00:05:51,434
[imitates mattress creaking]

130
00:05:52,727 --> 00:05:55,688
‎抱歉 我喜欢让人不舒服
Sorry. I love making people
feel uncomfortable.

131
00:05:56,397 --> 00:05:57,774
‎你挺厉害的
You're really good at it. [scoffs]

132
00:05:59,484 --> 00:06:02,278
‎总之 给我讲讲芝加哥的事
‎你有什么爱好？
Anyway, tell me about Chicago.
What are you into?

133
00:06:02,362 --> 00:06:04,280
‎我？多了去了
Me? Uh, a lot of stuff.

134
00:06:05,740 --> 00:06:06,741
‎上学
School.

135
00:06:07,867 --> 00:06:08,785
‎可喜欢上学了
School's a big one.

136
00:06:09,911 --> 00:06:11,788
‎我在辩论俱乐部是个大人物
‎这点不容争辩
And I'm a pretty big deal in Debate Club.

137
00:06:12,288 --> 00:06:13,706
‎我在辩论俱乐部是个大人物
‎这点不容争辩
<i>That's </i>not up for debate. [chuckles]

138
00:06:14,582 --> 00:06:16,000
‎好吧 我没人气
Yeah, I'm not popular.

139
00:06:17,460 --> 00:06:18,503
‎很好
Good.

140
00:06:18,586 --> 00:06:19,712
‎有人气的都是衰人
Popular people suck.

141
00:06:20,588 --> 00:06:21,672
‎没错 衰得很
Yeah, they really do.

142
00:06:21,756 --> 00:06:23,049
‎这段可赞了
Ooh, this part's dope.

143
00:06:25,218 --> 00:06:27,178
[volume increases]

144
00:06:27,845 --> 00:06:28,805
‎见鬼 格温！
Damn it, Gwen!

145
00:06:28,888 --> 00:06:31,349
‎把这破玩意关小点 人家正剃毛呢
Turn that crap down. I'm trying to shave.

146
00:06:32,683 --> 00:06:35,478
‎我老哥 不是一个爸生的 他还行
Older brother. Different dads. He's cool.

147
00:06:35,561 --> 00:06:37,980
‎主要是他有辆面包车 还好欺负
Mostly 'cause he has a van,
and he's fun to mess with.

148
00:06:38,064 --> 00:06:40,066
‎看好了
-Watch this.
-[volume increases]

149
00:06:40,149 --> 00:06:43,027
‎说真的 格温 我差点把奶头剃了
Seriously, Gwen. I almost nicked my nerps.

150
00:06:43,111 --> 00:06:46,072
‎这叽叽歪歪的娘娘腔调 我越听越毛
This whiny vagina music is bumming me out!

151
00:06:46,155 --> 00:06:47,782
‎是吗 内特？
-[music stops]
-Oh yeah, Nate?

152
00:06:47,865 --> 00:06:50,868
‎我和我朋友要组建一支乐队
‎就叫“叽歪娘娘”
Me and my new friend are gonna
start a band and call it Whiny Vagina.

153
00:06:50,952 --> 00:06:53,955
‎那我也组个乐队 就叫“这名真傻缺”
I'm gonna start a band
and call it That's Stupid.

154
00:06:55,289 --> 00:06:56,332
‎不赖
Nice.

155
00:06:58,501 --> 00:06:59,919
[music resumes loudly]

156
00:07:00,002 --> 00:07:01,254
‎该死 格温！
[Nate] Damn it, Gwen!

157
00:07:03,089 --> 00:07:05,341
‎我就喜欢家里都是人
I love having the house full again.

158
00:07:05,425 --> 00:07:07,510
‎感觉…让我充满快乐
It just… It fills me with joy.

159
00:07:08,094 --> 00:07:10,221
‎等你走了 我就伤心了
And then you leave, and it's sad.

160
00:07:11,472 --> 00:07:13,057
‎然后 冬天就来了
And then winter comes.

161
00:07:14,142 --> 00:07:16,060
‎然后我去给妈妈上坟
And I visit Mom's grave.

162
00:07:16,811 --> 00:07:20,314
‎我给她讲家里满是亲人有多开心
And I tell her how much fun it was
when the house was full.

163
00:07:24,068 --> 00:07:26,195
‎-现在能把糖浆给我吗？
‎-当然
-So can I have the syrup now?
-Oh, of course.

164
00:07:27,196 --> 00:07:28,197
‎早安 拜拜
Morning. Bye.

165
00:07:28,281 --> 00:07:30,533
‎我说 你鼻子里那是什么玩意儿？
Whoa. What the hell is that thing
in your nose?

166
00:07:30,616 --> 00:07:31,492
‎鼻环？
Uh, a nose ring?

167
00:07:32,660 --> 00:07:33,911
‎看你的了 嫩皮娃娃
Your move, baby skin.

168
00:07:36,122 --> 00:07:37,999
‎-怎么会这样？
‎-是格温给我的
-How did this happen?
-Gwen gave it to me.

169
00:07:38,082 --> 00:07:40,710
‎是格温啊 好吧 我不知道是她
Oh! Okay, it was Gwen.
Cool. I didn't know it was Gwen.

170
00:07:40,793 --> 00:07:42,003
‎你离开之前 我有个问题
Question before you leave.

171
00:07:42,086 --> 00:07:44,589
‎格温是谁啊 她干嘛在你脸上戳洞？
Who is Gwen, and why is she
poking holes in your perfect face?

172
00:07:46,424 --> 00:07:49,010
‎她住在隔壁 我现在正要去那里
She lives next door,
which is where I'm going right now.

173
00:07:49,093 --> 00:07:51,429
‎-她父母在家吗？
‎-不 她哥哥在
-Are her parents home?
-No, but her older brother is.

174
00:07:51,512 --> 00:07:54,348
‎亲 你是在给自己挖坑
Honey, you're really
not helping your case.

175
00:07:56,267 --> 00:07:58,060
‎老爸 我离家也就六米远
Dad, I'll be 20 feet away.

176
00:07:58,936 --> 00:08:01,397
‎好吧 但你要赶回来看焰火
Okay, you can go, but you have to be
home in time for fireworks.

177
00:08:01,481 --> 00:08:02,440
‎-好吗？
‎-我尽量
-Okay?
-I'll try.

178
00:08:02,523 --> 00:08:03,441
Ah, ah, ah, ah!

179
00:08:03,524 --> 00:08:04,609
‎正如尤达大师所说…
As Master Yoda said--

180
00:08:04,692 --> 00:08:05,818
‎干嘛呀？
-Why?
-[Red grumbles]

181
00:08:05,902 --> 00:08:10,865
‎正如尤达大师所说：
‎“做或不做 没有尽量”
As Master Yoda said,
"Do or do not. There is no try."

182
00:08:10,948 --> 00:08:15,286
‎尤达大师是虚假世界里
‎一个被打了屁股的小人儿
Master Yoda was a puppet from a fake
world with some guy's hand up his butt.

183
00:08:16,954 --> 00:08:18,706
‎你就是故意说难听话
Now you're just being hurtful.

184
00:08:18,789 --> 00:08:20,708
‎十几岁的娃娃最难搞
Ah, teenagers!

185
00:08:20,791 --> 00:08:22,293
‎儿子 我同情你
I feel for you, son.

186
00:08:23,753 --> 00:08:25,296
‎不过话说回来
But, on the other hand,

187
00:08:25,963 --> 00:08:27,840
‎出来混 迟早要还的
payback's a bitch.

188
00:08:27,924 --> 00:08:31,886
[rock music playing]

189
00:08:35,640 --> 00:08:36,474
‎乌诺
Uno.

190
00:08:38,226 --> 00:08:40,311
‎你好像只能放一张牌
I think you're only allowed
to drop one card.

191
00:08:40,394 --> 00:08:41,395
‎什么？
Excuse me?

192
00:08:43,940 --> 00:08:44,857
‎地下室真不赖
Cool basement.

193
00:08:44,941 --> 00:08:45,775
‎这里就是垃圾场
It's a dump.

194
00:08:46,984 --> 00:08:48,194
‎无意冒犯
No offense.

195
00:08:49,028 --> 00:08:51,155
‎奥兹和我是去年留堂时认识的
Ozzie and I met last year in detention.

196
00:08:51,239 --> 00:08:52,323
‎跟她说说你干了啥
Tell her what you did.

197
00:08:52,406 --> 00:08:55,076
‎我跟我的数学老师说他老婆出轨
I told my math teacher
his wife was cheating on him.

198
00:08:55,159 --> 00:08:57,078
‎她跟别的汉子在“国际松饼之家”亲热
She was making out with some dude at IHOP.

199
00:08:57,161 --> 00:08:59,121
‎-太可怕了
‎-就是
-That's horrible.
-[Ozzie] I know.

200
00:08:59,205 --> 00:09:00,456
‎“国际松饼之家” 拜托有点档次
IHOP.

201
00:09:00,540 --> 00:09:01,916
‎“国际松饼之家” 拜托有点档次
Show some class.

202
00:09:01,999 --> 00:09:03,084
[running footsteps]

203
00:09:03,167 --> 00:09:06,045
‎你们肯定不信 我遇上的事赞爆了
You're not gonna believe what happened.
It's the best thing ever!

204
00:09:06,128 --> 00:09:08,756
‎烤制猪排堡回归的时候 你也这么说
That's what you said
when the McRib came back.

205
00:09:08,839 --> 00:09:10,466
‎妮可 我还以为再也吃不着了呢
I thought it was gone forever, Nik.

206
00:09:10,550 --> 00:09:12,468
‎你害怕了？
Aww! You were scared?

207
00:09:13,135 --> 00:09:14,804
‎哦 宝贝
Oh, babe.

208
00:09:21,394 --> 00:09:22,228
‎嘿 新来的妹子
Hey, new girl.

209
00:09:23,604 --> 00:09:24,939
‎嘿 小子
Hey, boy. [chuckles]

210
00:09:26,899 --> 00:09:27,733
‎小伙子？
Man…?

211
00:09:28,859 --> 00:09:31,237
‎我不知道你青春期过得咋样
‎应该不赖吧
I don't know how
the whole puberty thing is going for you.

212
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,697
‎我不知道你青春期过得咋样
‎应该不赖吧
Probably great. [chuckles]

213
00:09:33,447 --> 00:09:34,574
‎莉亚 他叫杰伊
Leia, this is Jay.

214
00:09:35,074 --> 00:09:38,786
‎记得把你的拉链和扣子都系好拉上
Please place all your zippers and buttons
in their upright and locked positions.

215
00:09:38,869 --> 00:09:42,582
‎别这样 格温 我就是聊聊 交交心
Hey, not cool, Gwen. I'm just doing
a little get-to-know-you chitchat.

216
00:09:43,833 --> 00:09:44,667
‎说起来
So,

217
00:09:45,918 --> 00:09:47,003
‎你崇尚精神吗？
are you spiritual?

218
00:09:48,337 --> 00:09:49,171
‎反正我崇尚
I am.

219
00:09:50,423 --> 00:09:52,049
‎你又是那副样子
You're making a face.

220
00:09:52,133 --> 00:09:54,135
‎但这招对我挺管用
But that would have worked on me.

221
00:09:55,428 --> 00:09:57,138
‎我能讲我的精彩遭遇了吗？
Can I tell my awesome story now?

222
00:09:57,638 --> 00:09:59,849
‎我们就在我车里待着
So we were just chilling in my van.

223
00:10:00,349 --> 00:10:03,269
‎-为什么他总是坐在前面？
‎-因为我抢到了副驾
-Why does he always get to sit in front?
-I called shotgun.

224
00:10:03,352 --> 00:10:05,896
‎-我可是你女朋友
‎-没错 但他是我最好的朋友
-But I'm your girlfriend.
-Yeah, but he's my <i>best </i>friend.

225
00:10:07,648 --> 00:10:09,317
‎-兄弟
‎-兄弟
-Bro.
-Bro.

226
00:10:10,359 --> 00:10:11,360
‎兄弟
Bro.

227
00:10:13,112 --> 00:10:14,113
‎兄弟
Bro.

228
00:10:15,948 --> 00:10:18,284
‎老天 我居然为你拒绝了学长
Oh my God. I turned down a senior for you.

229
00:10:19,035 --> 00:10:21,495
‎对不住 宝贝 但你们俩对我都很重要
I'm sorry, babe,
but you're both important to me.

230
00:10:21,579 --> 00:10:23,748
‎12年来 杰伊都是我的后援
But Jay's had my back
for the past 12 years,

231
00:10:23,831 --> 00:10:27,293
‎而过去六个月 我的前庭都是你的
‎手心手背都是肉
and you've had my front
for the last six months. I can't choose.

232
00:10:27,376 --> 00:10:30,463
‎喂 你们是来取
‎“老妈折扣酒铺”的酒桶的吗？
Hey. Are you here to pick up the keg
from Mama's Discount Liquors?

233
00:10:33,090 --> 00:10:34,091
‎-没错
‎-没错
-Yes.
-Yes.

234
00:10:34,175 --> 00:10:35,426
‎而且你们预付了 对吧？
And you prepaid, right?

235
00:10:37,386 --> 00:10:38,220
‎-是的
‎-是的
-Yes.
-Yes.

236
00:10:38,304 --> 00:10:39,430
‎好得很
Sweet.

237
00:10:44,810 --> 00:10:45,728
‎独立日愉快
Happy Fourth.

238
00:10:48,773 --> 00:10:50,149
‎-兄弟！
‎-兄弟！
-Bro!
-Bro!

239
00:10:50,650 --> 00:10:51,567
‎-兄弟
‎-兄弟
-Bro.
-Bro.

240
00:10:51,651 --> 00:10:53,027
‎-兄弟
‎-兄弟
-Bro. Bro!
-Bro. Bro!

241
00:10:53,110 --> 00:10:53,986
‎-兄弟
‎-兄弟
-Bro!
-Bro.

242
00:10:54,070 --> 00:10:54,987
‎-兄弟
‎-兄弟
-Bro.
-Bro.

243
00:10:55,071 --> 00:10:56,697
‎他俩一路上就这样
They were like this the whole ride.

244
00:10:57,865 --> 00:11:00,868
‎拜托 宝贝 这可是独立日的奇迹
Come on, babe.
It's a Fourth of July miracle.

245
00:11:01,369 --> 00:11:02,203
‎而且还有啤酒
With beer!

246
00:11:02,286 --> 00:11:05,956
‎还在这里废话什么？
‎咱们一起喝他个烂醉如泥
Why are we still talking?
Let's tap that keg and get stupid!

247
00:11:06,040 --> 00:11:07,667
‎-对
‎-坏了
-Yeah.
-Oh no.

248
00:11:09,001 --> 00:11:10,211
‎我们没有酒头
We don't have a tap.

249
00:11:10,961 --> 00:11:13,673
‎没有酒头的话 啤酒就…出不来
And, without a tap,
the beer is… is trapped.

250
00:11:14,465 --> 00:11:18,386
‎-亲一下感觉会好点吗？
‎-除非你嘴里全是啤酒
-Would a kiss make it better?
-Not unless you have a mouth full of beer.

251
00:11:20,471 --> 00:11:22,098
‎-是吗？
‎-不是
-Do you?
-No, I don't.

252
00:11:22,181 --> 00:11:25,559
[rock music playing]

253
00:11:28,145 --> 00:11:29,271
‎这感觉好奇怪
This feels weird.

254
00:11:30,606 --> 00:11:32,692
‎很不一样
Very different.

255
00:11:33,484 --> 00:11:35,027
‎我反正挺高兴的
Well, I'm having fun.

256
00:11:37,279 --> 00:11:38,781
‎怎么烟熏火燎的？
Why is it so smoky?

257
00:11:39,699 --> 00:11:41,325
‎天啊 爆米花
Oh God, the popcorn!

258
00:11:42,702 --> 00:11:44,995
‎孩子们 玩得开心吗？
Enjoying yourselves, kids?

259
00:11:45,955 --> 00:11:48,040
‎你们现在也在楼上耍了
You're upstairs people now.

260
00:11:49,417 --> 00:11:50,918
‎我就知道会这样
I knew it would happen.

261
00:11:51,419 --> 00:11:52,753
‎只是没想到这么快
Just not this soon.

262
00:11:54,630 --> 00:11:57,049
‎别担心了 艾瑞克 莉亚不会有事的
Quit worrying, Eric. Leia will be fine.

263
00:11:57,758 --> 00:11:59,343
‎你现在能预知未来了吗？
So now you can tell the future?

264
00:11:59,427 --> 00:12:01,929
‎我买那双滑溜溜的棕色鞋子时
‎你在哪里呢？
Where were you when I bought
those slippery brown shoes?

265
00:12:02,012 --> 00:12:03,931
‎-我连机场的坡道都上不去
‎-好了 艾瑞克
I couldn't get up the ramp at the airport.

266
00:12:04,014 --> 00:12:05,099
‎-我连机场的坡道都上不去
‎-好了 艾瑞克
[Donna] Okay, Eric.

267
00:12:08,144 --> 00:12:09,395
‎不给你喝果酒了
No more Zima for you.

268
00:12:10,604 --> 00:12:12,898
‎你说得对 我都喝飘了
Yeah, you're right. I'm… I'm flying.

269
00:12:14,108 --> 00:12:15,609
‎多数爆米花都还好
I saved most of it.

270
00:12:15,693 --> 00:12:16,861
‎谢谢 妈妈
Ah. Thanks, Mom.

271
00:12:17,820 --> 00:12:18,654
‎“妈妈”
"Mom."

272
00:12:19,155 --> 00:12:21,157
‎看到没 多好叫啊 唐娜？
You see how easy it is, Donna?

273
00:12:22,742 --> 00:12:24,744
‎叫一声不就完了？
Can't you just say it?

274
00:12:25,828 --> 00:12:27,830
‎不要 感觉像被迫的
Nah. Feels forced.

275
00:12:28,581 --> 00:12:30,082
‎拜托 妈妈 别纠结了
Come on, Mom, just drop it.

276
00:12:30,958 --> 00:12:31,876
‎不要 感觉像被迫的
Nah.

277
00:12:32,376 --> 00:12:33,586
‎不要 感觉像被迫的
Feels forced.

278
00:12:37,006 --> 00:12:40,176
[rock music playing]

279
00:12:41,093 --> 00:12:42,344
‎小屁孩对阵啤酒
Kids versus beer.

280
00:12:43,095 --> 00:12:44,722
‎一个亘古不变的传说
It's a tale as old as time.

281
00:12:45,306 --> 00:12:48,809
‎父母 祖辈 无不如此
It happened to our parents
and our parents' parents.

282
00:12:48,893 --> 00:12:50,269
‎“五月花号”上的孩子们
The kids on the Mayflower.

283
00:12:50,770 --> 00:12:54,356
‎奥兹 你好烦 我正想办法呢
Ozzie. You're killing me, man.
I'm trying to think here.

284
00:12:54,440 --> 00:12:56,484
‎我知道 闻得出来
I know. I can smell it.

285
00:12:57,818 --> 00:13:01,530
‎等等 为什么不回“老妈”那里
‎去买酒头呢？
Wait, why can't we just
go back to Mama's and get a tap?

286
00:13:02,114 --> 00:13:04,658
‎我们都试过去她家买酒 但她很难搞
We've all tried to buy from her,
but she's tough.

287
00:13:04,742 --> 00:13:06,702
‎我还试着跟她搭讪说：
I mean, I even hit her with the,

288
00:13:08,120 --> 00:13:09,121
‎“嘿 妹子”
"Hey, girl."

289
00:13:10,039 --> 00:13:10,873
‎啥用都没有
Nothing.

290
00:13:12,124 --> 00:13:15,127
‎-如果我们用激光呢？
‎-我们没有激光
-What if we get a laser?
-We're not getting a laser.

291
00:13:16,086 --> 00:13:18,214
‎那就这样了 能试的都试了
Well, I guess that's it.
We tried everything.

292
00:13:18,297 --> 00:13:20,549
‎你就说了一个主意 还蠢得要命
You said one idea, and it was stupid.

293
00:13:20,633 --> 00:13:21,592
‎你才蠢
You're stupid!

294
00:13:21,675 --> 00:13:24,595
‎你们都蠢 你们讨厌啤酒 讨厌美国
You're all stupid!
You hate beer and you hate America.

295
00:13:24,678 --> 00:13:25,971
‎-宝贝？
‎-嗯？
-Baby?
-Yeah?

296
00:13:26,055 --> 00:13:27,556
‎你是不是很沮丧？
Are you feeling frustrated?

297
00:13:27,640 --> 00:13:28,474
‎嗯
Yeah.

298
00:13:28,557 --> 00:13:31,894
‎-所以你就跟别人发脾气？
‎-嗯
-Is this why you're lashing out at others?
-Yeah.

299
00:13:33,479 --> 00:13:37,525
‎咱们明天进小树林
‎我看你对着树打空手道怎么样？
How about tomorrow we go into the woods,
and I watch you do karate on a tree?

300
00:13:37,608 --> 00:13:38,859
‎好得很
-I'd really like that.
-Oh.

301
00:13:40,528 --> 00:13:41,987
‎你们这些笨蛋闹够了没？
Are you dill weeds finished?

302
00:13:42,071 --> 00:13:45,324
‎莉亚 你去买 老妈还不认识你
Leia, you should buy the tap.
Mama doesn't know you.

303
00:13:45,407 --> 00:13:47,201
‎对啊 你肯定能行
Oh yeah. You totally could.

304
00:13:47,284 --> 00:13:50,120
‎再说 你眼睛美得要命
‎虽然买酒头用不上
Plus, your eyes are crazy pretty,
which won't really help get the tap,

305
00:13:50,204 --> 00:13:51,789
‎但我还是注意到了
but it's something I noticed.

306
00:13:53,207 --> 00:13:54,750
‎嘿 妹子
-Hey, girl.
-[scoffs]

307
00:13:55,709 --> 00:13:58,587
‎莉亚 这可屌爆了
Leia, it would be so badass.

308
00:13:59,171 --> 00:14:01,340
‎我也做过一些疯狂的事
I guess I have done
some pretty crazy things.

309
00:14:01,423 --> 00:14:04,301
‎一次在海边
‎一只海鸥偷了我的三明治
One time at the beach,
a seagull stole my sandwich,

310
00:14:04,385 --> 00:14:08,055
‎我小声骂她“贱货”
and, under my breath,
I… called her "bitch."

311
00:14:10,891 --> 00:14:12,309
‎你们猜怎么的？我去
You know what? I'm in.

312
00:14:12,893 --> 00:14:14,478
‎好得很 新妹子真牛
All right. New girl is sick.

313
00:14:14,562 --> 00:14:16,105
‎-上车
‎-稍等
-To the van!
-Pause.

314
00:14:17,398 --> 00:14:18,774
‎这样行不通
This isn't gonna work.

315
00:14:18,858 --> 00:14:21,443
‎见到这童装女
‎人家肯定要看她身份证
I'm pretty sure OshKosh B'gosh here
is gonna get carded.

316
00:14:22,987 --> 00:14:23,988
‎有道理
Good point.

317
00:14:25,072 --> 00:14:26,073
‎我有个主意
I have an idea.

318
00:14:31,662 --> 00:14:33,956
‎亲 你都这样了 确定要喝酒吗？
You sure you want to be drinking
in your condition, hon?

319
00:14:34,039 --> 00:14:35,457
‎我是给我老公的买的
‎酒桶是给宝宝派对准备的
Oh, it's… [nervous chuckle]

320
00:14:35,541 --> 00:14:38,961
‎我是给我老公的买的
‎酒桶是给宝宝派对准备的
It's for my husband.
He… He got a keg for the baby shower.

321
00:14:39,837 --> 00:14:41,380
‎好高级
Oh, fancy.

322
00:14:42,590 --> 00:14:43,549
[register beeping]

323
00:14:43,632 --> 00:14:45,968
‎-一共39块5
‎-好的
-That'll be $39.50.
-Okay.

324
00:14:50,014 --> 00:14:53,559
‎我不是什么妇科大夫
‎但你这肚子瞅着不对劲
I'm no lady doctor, but I think
something's wrong with the baby.

325
00:14:55,352 --> 00:14:56,186
‎想得美
Nice try.

326
00:14:56,270 --> 00:14:58,480
‎真受够你们这帮小屁孩了
‎我这就报警
I'm sick of you kids.
I'm calling the cops.

327
00:14:59,523 --> 00:15:01,483
‎老妈 把电话放下
Put the phone down, Mama.

328
00:15:01,567 --> 00:15:02,693
‎闭嘴
Shut up.

329
00:15:02,776 --> 00:15:04,570
‎好吧 等警察来了
Fine, but when the cops get here,

330
00:15:04,653 --> 00:15:08,240
‎你要怎么跟他们解释
‎为什么你把一桶酒给了一群孩子？
how are you gonna explain to them
why you gave a keg to a bunch of kids?

331
00:15:08,324 --> 00:15:09,909
‎不是我 是韦德干的
It wasn't me. It was Wade.

332
00:15:09,992 --> 00:15:10,868
‎老妈
Mama!

333
00:15:12,828 --> 00:15:15,539
‎无论如何 你都会被吊销卖酒执照
Either way, you lose your liquor license.

334
00:15:15,623 --> 00:15:20,961
‎所以把电话放下 把酒头卖给我
‎大家高高兴兴过个独立日
So put the phone down, sell me the tap,
and we all have a nice Fourth of July.

335
00:15:24,214 --> 00:15:26,050
‎你是干嘛的 当律师吗？
What are you, some sort of lawyer?

336
00:15:26,133 --> 00:15:29,303
‎辩论俱乐部 初中地区赛第一名
Debate Club.
First place, junior regionals.

337
00:15:29,386 --> 00:15:31,013
‎你根本不是我的对手
It was over before it started.

338
00:15:31,096 --> 00:15:32,389
[gasps]

339
00:15:32,473 --> 00:15:36,602
[rock music playing]

340
00:15:36,685 --> 00:15:39,313
‎敬老妈克星 莉亚！
To Leia, the Mama slayer!

341
00:15:39,396 --> 00:15:40,773
‎敬莉亚！
[all] To Leia!

342
00:15:40,856 --> 00:15:43,317
‎也敬扎波尔斯基老师
And to Mrs. Zapolski. [chuckles]

343
00:15:43,400 --> 00:15:46,111
‎我在辩论俱乐部的教练
‎每天逼着我练
My Debate Club coach,
for pushing me so damn hard.

344
00:15:46,195 --> 00:15:48,489
‎敬扎波尔斯基老师！
[all] To Mrs. Zapolski!

345
00:15:49,698 --> 00:15:53,327
‎快看 妮可 是流星 快许愿
Wow. Look, Nik, a shooting star.
Make a wish.

346
00:15:53,410 --> 00:15:54,745
‎亲 那是焰火表演
That's a firework, babe.

347
00:15:54,828 --> 00:15:56,121
[fireworks whistling and popping]

348
00:15:56,205 --> 00:15:59,792
‎天啊 你今晚真是太牛了
‎没想到你还有这一面
Man, you were such a badass tonight.
I didn't know you had it in you.

349
00:16:00,292 --> 00:16:04,254
‎我也没想到 但我喜欢这种感觉
Neither did I, but I love this feeling.

350
00:16:04,338 --> 00:16:08,968
‎感觉很自由 很开心
‎真希望我能留在这里过暑假
I feel free and happy.
Wish I could stay for the summer.

351
00:16:10,135 --> 00:16:11,136
‎那就留下吧
Then stay.

352
00:16:11,220 --> 00:16:13,305
‎我爸不会同意的
[snickers] My dad will never let me.

353
00:16:14,014 --> 00:16:15,599
‎我爸妈离婚的时候
When my parents split up,

354
00:16:15,683 --> 00:16:19,478
‎学校的心理医生说我会丧一辈子
the school shrink basically told me
that everything was gonna suck forever,

355
00:16:19,979 --> 00:16:23,357
‎我心想：“我才不要”
and I was like, "Nope. Not this girl."

356
00:16:23,440 --> 00:16:26,402
‎于是我回到家
‎在洗衣机顶上漂了头发
So I went home, bleached my hair
over the washing machine,

357
00:16:26,485 --> 00:16:29,071
‎剪开牛仔裤 下定决心 这是我的人生
cut up my jeans
and decided that this is <i>my</i> life,

358
00:16:29,154 --> 00:16:30,489
‎我绝对不会丧下去
and it's <i>never </i>gonna suck.

359
00:16:32,866 --> 00:16:34,827
‎这话听起来有点傻
This is gonna sound so dorky,

360
00:16:34,910 --> 00:16:38,247
‎但是…我有点想跟你成为好友
but… I'm interested in
us becoming best friends,

361
00:16:38,330 --> 00:16:39,707
‎我该怎么做呢？
so how do we make that happen?

362
00:16:40,582 --> 00:16:41,792
‎留下来过暑假
Stay for the summer.

363
00:16:42,710 --> 00:16:45,337
‎你也用不着傻话免责声明
‎已经暗含了
And you can drop the dorky disclaimer.
It's implied.

364
00:16:45,421 --> 00:16:46,380
[chuckles]

365
00:16:46,964 --> 00:16:48,257
‎好得很
Oh great.

366
00:16:48,340 --> 00:16:50,968
‎她错过了焰火表演和香肠
Now she's missed the fireworks
and the weenies.

367
00:16:51,051 --> 00:16:55,305
‎它们冷冰冰皱巴巴躺在盘子里
‎就像我的心一样
Now they're sitting on a plate
all cold and shriveled just like my heart.

368
00:16:55,806 --> 00:16:57,933
‎艾瑞克
Oh, Eric.

369
00:16:58,017 --> 00:17:00,269
‎妈 闻头发还是很诡异
The hair thing,
it's still a little weird, Mom.

370
00:17:00,811 --> 00:17:03,355
‎最糟糕的是什么？
‎我该珍惜与莉亚共度的时光
Know what the worst part is?
I should be treasuring time with Leia.

371
00:17:03,439 --> 00:17:06,066
‎结果我…却巴不得这段时光赶紧结束
Instead, I mean,
I… can't wait for it to end.

372
00:17:06,650 --> 00:17:07,985
‎亲爱的 等你死了就结束了
Oh, sweetie.

373
00:17:08,068 --> 00:17:09,987
‎亲爱的 等你死了就结束了
It ends when you die.

374
00:17:13,532 --> 00:17:15,784
‎莉亚塔图因福尔曼
Leia Tatooine Forman.

375
00:17:16,660 --> 00:17:19,329
‎-她的中间名是安妮
‎-我可没答应
-Her middle name is Anne.
-Know what? I never agreed to that.

376
00:17:19,830 --> 00:17:22,332
‎你去哪里了？
‎我的天啊 那是啤酒吗？
Where have you been?
Oh my God. Is that beer?

377
00:17:22,416 --> 00:17:25,419
‎是的 从水塔下来时
‎把杯里剩下的全给洒了
Yeah. And I spilled the rest
coming down the water tower.

378
00:17:25,502 --> 00:17:27,671
‎呃…水塔？搞什么？
The… water tower? What the hell?

379
00:17:27,755 --> 00:17:29,089
‎艾瑞克 我来处理 水塔？搞什么？
Eric, let me handle this.

380
00:17:29,173 --> 00:17:30,799
‎艾瑞克 我来处理 水塔？搞什么？
The water tower? What the hell?

381
00:17:30,883 --> 00:17:33,302
‎这才是我喜欢的焰火
Now, this is <i>my </i>kind of fireworks.

382
00:17:35,637 --> 00:17:37,097
‎对 水塔
Yes, the water tower.

383
00:17:37,181 --> 00:17:40,017
‎我玩得很开心 我还想继续
And I had a great time
and I don't want it to end.

384
00:17:40,517 --> 00:17:42,394
‎我知道你们会不高兴
So I know you're not
gonna like me saying this,

385
00:17:42,478 --> 00:17:44,980
‎但…我想留在点域镇过暑假
but… I want to stay in Point Place
for the summer.

386
00:17:45,564 --> 00:17:47,983
‎这是我的生活
‎我不想过得这么没意思
This is my life,
and I'm done letting it suck.

387
00:17:48,067 --> 00:17:49,276
‎-莉亚
‎-对 你上
-Leia.
-Yeah, go.

388
00:17:49,359 --> 00:17:51,403
‎别憋着 亲 全面出击
Just unload, baby. Both barrels. Go.

389
00:17:52,780 --> 00:17:55,032
‎-你很有胆量 我很佩服
‎-啥？
-That took courage. I'm impressed.
-What?!

390
00:17:55,115 --> 00:17:56,950
‎这主意太荒谬了
Th-This is a ridiculous idea.

391
00:17:57,034 --> 00:17:59,369
‎-莉亚
‎-妈 你上 说说她
-Leia.
-Mom, just go, preach.

392
00:17:59,453 --> 00:18:02,498
‎如果你想留下来 我们当然欢迎
You are welcome to stay here
if that's what you want.

393
00:18:02,581 --> 00:18:04,249
‎我的天！什么情况？
Oh my God! What's happening?

394
00:18:04,333 --> 00:18:05,167
‎凯蒂
Kitty.

395
00:18:06,585 --> 00:18:08,712
‎我想这就是我们想要的
I guess that's what we want.

396
00:18:11,381 --> 00:18:13,133
‎老爸 你们总是说
Dad, you guys always talk about

397
00:18:13,217 --> 00:18:15,219
‎小时候跟朋友在一起有多开心
the amazing times
you had with your friends.

398
00:18:15,302 --> 00:18:17,262
‎我也想要 我也想开心
I want that. I want amazing.

399
00:18:17,346 --> 00:18:19,264
‎听着 伙计 短短一天之内
Listen, pal. In the space of one day,

400
00:18:19,348 --> 00:18:22,017
‎你穿了洞 喝了酒 现在又…这么嘚瑟
you've gotten pierced, you've gotten beer,
and you've gotten

401
00:18:22,643 --> 00:18:24,311
‎你穿了洞 喝了酒 现在又…这么嘚瑟
extremely snippy.

402
00:18:24,978 --> 00:18:27,272
‎你变得我都不认识了
You've turned into someone
that I don't know anymore.

403
00:18:27,356 --> 00:18:29,024
‎不行 知道吗？想都别想
So no. You know what? You can forget it.

404
00:18:29,108 --> 00:18:30,859
‎我就知道你会这样
I knew you were gonna be like this.

405
00:18:30,943 --> 00:18:32,903
‎明天我不会上那辆车 你强迫不了我
I'm not getting in that car tomorrow!
You can't make me!

406
00:18:32,986 --> 00:18:35,614
‎你给我乖乖上车 不然我打你屁股
Oh, you're getting in that car
or my foot is getting in your ass!

407
00:18:38,826 --> 00:18:41,620
‎-哦 艾瑞克
‎-太逊了
-Oh, Eric.
-So bad.

408
00:18:42,663 --> 00:18:45,207
‎我现在骄傲到不行
I have never been prouder.

409
00:18:46,542 --> 00:18:50,170
‎就好像看着你第一次打全垒打
It's like watching you hit
your first home run.

410
00:18:51,296 --> 00:18:52,589
‎当然 如果你打过的话
If you had ever done that.

411
00:18:53,674 --> 00:18:57,344
[soft guitar music playing]

412
00:18:57,427 --> 00:18:59,263
[crickets chirping]

413
00:19:01,181 --> 00:19:02,182
‎你没事吧？
You okay?

414
00:19:03,267 --> 00:19:04,393
‎真不敢相信
I can't believe it.

415
00:19:04,476 --> 00:19:07,187
‎我研究了一辈子《星球大战》
‎结果到了关键时刻
I study <i>Star Wars</i> my entire life,
and in my moment of truth,

416
00:19:07,271 --> 00:19:09,523
‎我却变成了自己的邪恶老爸
I turn into my evil father.

417
00:19:12,818 --> 00:19:13,986
‎我考虑过了
I've thought about it.

418
00:19:14,486 --> 00:19:17,781
‎莉亚留下来也不会太离谱
‎毕竟你父母会照看她
Leia staying isn't the craziest idea.
Your parents can watch her.

419
00:19:17,865 --> 00:19:19,700
‎70年代 咱们不也一起在这里吗？
Were you not here with me in the '70s?

420
00:19:19,783 --> 00:19:21,410
‎让他们看孩子可不靠谱
They are not the best watchers.

421
00:19:22,494 --> 00:19:23,662
‎她是好孩子
She's a great kid.

422
00:19:25,956 --> 00:19:26,832
‎是啊 我知道
Yeah, I know.

423
00:19:26,915 --> 00:19:28,167
‎我们可以相信她
We can trust her.

424
00:19:28,250 --> 00:19:29,293
‎我知道
I know.

425
00:19:29,793 --> 00:19:31,044
‎所以呢？
So what, then?

426
00:19:31,128 --> 00:19:32,296
‎我只是…
I just…

427
00:19:32,379 --> 00:19:35,174
‎她不再需要我了 这让我受不了
I mean, I can't stand this feeling.
She doesn't need me anymore.

428
00:19:36,091 --> 00:19:38,510
‎我是说 她一直是我的小伙伴
‎而现在却变得像是…
I mean, she was my little buddy,
and now she's like

429
00:19:39,428 --> 00:19:40,596
‎陌生人
a stranger.

430
00:19:40,679 --> 00:19:44,308
‎她不是陌生人 她只是…长大了
She's not a stranger.
She's just… growing up.

431
00:19:45,726 --> 00:19:46,560
‎我不喜欢
I don't like it.

432
00:19:46,643 --> 00:19:49,688
‎什么？可你那么擅长隐藏自己的感情
What? But you're so good
at hiding your emotions.

433
00:19:49,771 --> 00:19:51,023
[both chuckle]

434
00:19:52,983 --> 00:19:54,610
‎没事的 艾瑞克
Eric, it's gonna be okay.

435
00:19:55,777 --> 00:19:56,820
‎你父母给了我们空间
‎让我们找到彼此 共度人生
We have our whole lives

436
00:19:56,904 --> 00:19:59,323
‎你父母给了我们空间
‎让我们找到彼此 共度人生
because your parents
gave us the space to find each other.

437
00:20:01,408 --> 00:20:02,409
‎真的吗？
Really?

438
00:20:02,492 --> 00:20:05,913
‎你家就距离六米远
‎咱俩肯定会找到彼此
You lived 20 feet away. I'm pretty sure
we would have found each other.

439
00:20:07,706 --> 00:20:10,792
[soft guitar music playing]

440
00:20:19,801 --> 00:20:20,802
‎嘿
Hey.

441
00:20:21,637 --> 00:20:22,638
‎干嘛？
What?

442
00:20:23,347 --> 00:20:25,891
‎-你的鼻环呢？
‎-那就是一块磁铁
-Oh, what happened to the nose ring?
-It was a magnet.

443
00:20:25,974 --> 00:20:27,976
‎我打了个喷嚏 它掉进下水道了
I sneezed and it went down the drain.

444
00:20:28,060 --> 00:20:29,061
Ah.

445
00:20:30,270 --> 00:20:31,980
‎哎呀 好可惜
Well, I'm… I'm heartbroken.

446
00:20:33,273 --> 00:20:34,399
‎我在你这么大的时候
‎我和朋友们成天宅在这间地下室
Back when I was your age,

447
00:20:34,483 --> 00:20:36,860
‎我在你这么大的时候
‎我和朋友们成天宅在这间地下室
my friends and I pretty much
lived down in this basement.

448
00:20:36,944 --> 00:20:41,073
‎我们一起打发时间 听音乐
‎做些…其他事情
We'd kill time, listen to music,
do… other things.

449
00:20:42,449 --> 00:20:46,119
‎坐在那边的楼梯上 我爱上了你妈妈
Sitting on those stairs right there
when I fell in love with your mom.

450
00:20:47,120 --> 00:20:49,456
‎老天 你们还在楼梯上做过？
Oh God. Did you do it on those stairs too?

451
00:20:49,539 --> 00:20:50,499
‎没有
No.

452
00:20:53,877 --> 00:20:54,878
‎没有
No.

453
00:20:56,713 --> 00:20:58,757
‎听着 我考虑过了…
Look, I've been thinking about it, and…

454
00:21:01,343 --> 00:21:03,303
‎你可以留下…过暑假
You should stay… for the summer.

455
00:21:04,805 --> 00:21:06,473
‎-你说真的吗？
‎-对
-Are you for real?
-Yeah.

456
00:21:07,224 --> 00:21:11,395
‎要说谁值得拥有…快乐 那就是你
If anyone deserves some… amazing,
it's you.

457
00:21:11,979 --> 00:21:15,774
‎我的天 谢谢爸爸
‎很抱歉 我刚才那么犯浑
Oh my God, Dad. Thank you.
Sorry I was kind of a jerk.

458
00:21:15,857 --> 00:21:18,151
‎没想到 在这方面 你还挺厉害的
Well, you were
surprisingly good at it. [chuckles]

459
00:21:19,486 --> 00:21:20,737
‎要知道…
But, you know, you're…

460
00:21:22,698 --> 00:21:23,699
‎你做什么都厉害
You're good at everything.

461
00:21:27,703 --> 00:21:28,829
‎我会想你的 伙计
I'll miss you, pal.

462
00:21:30,080 --> 00:21:31,581
‎我很爱你 知道吗？
I love you so much, okay?

463
00:21:33,125 --> 00:21:34,334
[sighs softly]

464
00:21:34,418 --> 00:21:36,003
‎你在闻我的头发吗？
Are you smelling my hair?

465
00:21:36,086 --> 00:21:37,421
‎没有
No.

466
00:21:38,505 --> 00:21:40,632
‎那也太诡异了
'Cause that would be weird.

467
00:21:42,384 --> 00:21:43,677
‎好了
[sniffs] Okay.

468
00:21:44,219 --> 00:21:47,556
[soft rock music playing]

469
00:21:50,851 --> 00:21:54,062
‎记住 我们的电话号码没变 好吗？
So just remember
our phone number hasn't changed, okay?

470
00:21:55,480 --> 00:21:57,774
‎别担心 亲爱的 我能搞定
Don't worry, honey. I got it.

471
00:21:58,400 --> 00:21:59,234
‎还是能搞定
Again.

472
00:22:00,569 --> 00:22:01,570
‎好的 亲爱的
Okay, babe.

473
00:22:03,405 --> 00:22:05,073
‎我的宝贝儿子
My baby boy.

474
00:22:05,574 --> 00:22:07,909
‎妈
Oh, uh… Mom.

475
00:22:07,993 --> 00:22:09,745
Shh!

476
00:22:09,828 --> 00:22:11,872
‎我在听你的心跳
I'm listening to your heartbeat.

477
00:22:13,165 --> 00:22:14,166
‎好吧 行了
Look. Okay.

478
00:22:19,713 --> 00:22:20,881
[Donna coos]

479
00:22:21,715 --> 00:22:22,632
‎爱你哟 莉莉
Love you, Le-Le.

480
00:22:22,716 --> 00:22:23,633
‎再见 妈妈
Bye, Mom.

481
00:22:24,760 --> 00:22:27,888
‎别担心 我们会玩得很开心的
Don't worry. We're gonna have fun.

482
00:22:27,971 --> 00:22:29,306
‎你清理过烤箱吗？
You ever cleaned an oven?

483
00:22:30,432 --> 00:22:31,433
‎祝你好运
Good luck.

484
00:22:32,309 --> 00:22:35,187
‎还有一件事 莉亚 这事…真的很重要
And one more thing, Leia.
This one's… really important.

485
00:22:35,270 --> 00:22:38,607
‎你跟你的新朋友
‎尽量多去爷爷的地下室
With your new friends, I want you
to hang out in Grandpa's basement

486
00:22:38,690 --> 00:22:40,192
‎尽量在那里玩
as much as possible.

487
00:22:40,275 --> 00:22:42,361
‎不 不可能
No. Uh-uh. No way.

488
00:22:42,444 --> 00:22:44,154
‎对她来说 那里最安全
It is the safest place for her.

489
00:22:44,237 --> 00:22:47,240
‎没错 妈妈 就是这样
That's right, Mom. That's so right.

490
00:22:47,324 --> 00:22:48,950
‎儿子 你够狠
Nicely played, son.

491
00:22:49,034 --> 00:22:50,327
‎名师出高徒嘛
I learned from the best.

492
00:22:50,410 --> 00:22:51,870
‎没人喜欢马屁精
Nobody likes an ass-kisser.

493
00:22:54,206 --> 00:22:55,123
‎我也爱你 老爸
I love you too, Dad.

494
00:22:57,584 --> 00:22:58,585
‎再见 妈
Bye, Mom.

495
00:23:01,546 --> 00:23:03,215
‎她叫“妈”了
She said "Mom."

496
00:23:05,175 --> 00:23:06,343
‎我赢了
I win.

497
00:23:07,511 --> 00:23:09,721
‎所以说嘛 别跟行家叫板
That's why you don't mess with a pro.

498
00:23:10,806 --> 00:23:15,143
[rock music playing]

499
00:23:15,227 --> 00:23:17,771
‎我得列张购物清单
Well, I have to make a shopping list.

500
00:23:17,854 --> 00:23:19,606
‎孩子们肯定要吃零食
The kids are gonna want snacks.

501
00:23:19,689 --> 00:23:21,441
‎凯蒂 别给他们准备吃的
Don't feed them, Kitty.

502
00:23:21,525 --> 00:23:23,819
‎后面就收不住了
That's how it started the first time.

503
00:23:24,403 --> 00:23:26,571
‎嗨 我和朋友们要去湖边
Hey. Me and my friends
are going up to the lake.

504
00:23:26,655 --> 00:23:27,489
‎等一下
[Red] Hold on.

505
00:23:28,281 --> 00:23:30,117
‎-你是谁？
‎-我是杰伊
-Who are you?
-I'm Jay.

506
00:23:31,576 --> 00:23:32,953
‎-杰伊凯尔索
‎-不
-Jay Kelso.
-No!

507
00:23:33,912 --> 00:23:35,038
Uh-uh!

508
00:23:35,122 --> 00:23:36,164
‎不行
No way!

509
00:23:36,248 --> 00:23:38,375
‎呛爆啦！
Buuuurn!

510
00:23:42,295 --> 00:23:43,296
Ahh!

511
00:23:43,380 --> 00:23:45,757
‎见到我儿子了吧？瞅瞅这小子
See you met my boy here, huh?
Look at this guy. Look at him.

512
00:23:45,841 --> 00:23:48,301
‎继承了他爹的长相和他妈的脑子
Look, he's got his dad's looks
and his mom's brains.

513
00:23:48,385 --> 00:23:49,719
‎去年的优等生
Straight A's last year.

514
00:23:49,803 --> 00:23:51,888
‎老天爷 人类在进化
Sweet Lord, it's evolving.

515
00:23:51,972 --> 00:23:53,014
[Kelso chuckles]

516
00:23:53,807 --> 00:23:55,809
‎你们一起好好玩儿 知道吗？
Hey, you kids. You have fun now, okay?

517
00:23:55,892 --> 00:23:58,061
‎如果要从悬崖往下跳 最好光着身子
Oh, and if you jump off that cliff,

518
00:23:58,145 --> 00:23:59,187
‎如果要从悬崖往下跳 最好光着身子
do it naked.

519
00:23:59,271 --> 00:24:01,731
‎好吗？如果入水角度合适的话
Okay? 'Cause when you hit the water
at the right angle,

520
00:24:01,815 --> 00:24:03,275
‎感觉就像打炮
it's like doing it with a lake.

521
00:24:07,654 --> 00:24:08,697
‎你好 麦克尔
Hello, Michael.

522
00:24:08,780 --> 00:24:09,656
‎嘿 妹子
Hey, girl.

523
00:24:09,739 --> 00:24:11,491
[Kitty giggles]

524
00:24:11,575 --> 00:24:13,285
Beautiful! [yells, laughs]

525
00:24:13,368 --> 00:24:14,661
[Kitty laughs]

526
00:24:15,912 --> 00:24:19,666
‎诶哟 这感觉…有年代 还暖烘烘的
-Well, that felt… toned and warm.
-[Kelso] Oh.

527
00:24:21,084 --> 00:24:21,918
‎我说 雷德
So, Red,

528
00:24:22,502 --> 00:24:25,672
‎我们得聊聊你孙女对我儿子的企图
we need to talk about your granddaughter's
intentions with my boy.

529
00:24:27,174 --> 00:24:29,801
‎没有 逗你玩呢 来抱一个
No, I'm just kidding ya.
Come on. Let's hug it out.

530
00:24:29,885 --> 00:24:31,136
‎你觉得呢？
What do you think?

531
00:24:32,012 --> 00:24:33,472
‎走啦 麦克尔！
Michael, let's go!

532
00:24:35,056 --> 00:24:35,974
‎嗨 凯蒂
Hi, Kitty.

533
00:24:37,017 --> 00:24:40,020
‎该死 杰姬 你就让我享受一会行吗？
Damn, Jackie, will you just
give me a minute to enjoy this?

534
00:24:40,103 --> 00:24:41,021
‎我的天啊
Oh my God.

535
00:24:41,521 --> 00:24:44,107
‎雷德额头上的血管都快爆了
The vein on Red's forehead
is about to explode.

536
00:24:45,484 --> 00:24:49,488
‎真恶心 我可不想
‎让老头的血溅在我的婚礼套服上
Gross! I don't want old guy blood
all over my wedding outfit.

537
00:24:49,571 --> 00:24:50,906
‎你俩要结婚了？
You're getting married?

538
00:24:50,989 --> 00:24:52,407
‎再婚
Remarried.

539
00:24:52,491 --> 00:24:54,409
‎-对 这是我们第二次再婚
‎-嗯哼
-Yeah, it's our second remarriage.
-Mm-hmm.

540
00:24:55,702 --> 00:24:57,537
‎-这次会坚持下去 对吧？
‎-对
-This one's gonna stick, right?
-Yeah.

541
00:24:59,372 --> 00:25:00,707
‎杰姬
Jackie.

542
00:25:00,790 --> 00:25:01,958
‎亲 穿白色哇？
White, honey?

543
00:25:03,668 --> 00:25:04,836
‎真的吗？
Really?

544
00:25:04,920 --> 00:25:06,838
‎劳动节还没过呢
It's before Labor Day.

545
00:25:07,339 --> 00:25:10,467
‎如果人们以为我们是初婚
‎我们收到的礼物会更好
And, if people think it's our first time,
we'll get better gifts.

546
00:25:10,550 --> 00:25:14,095
‎顺便说一句 我们在
‎布鲁明戴尔百货注册了 我很挑剔哦
Oh! FYI, we're registered
at Bloomingdale's,

547
00:25:14,179 --> 00:25:15,222
‎顺便说一句 我们在
‎布鲁明戴尔百货注册了 我很挑剔哦
and I will judge.

548
00:25:15,305 --> 00:25:17,724
‎-走啦 麦克尔！
‎-老天爷！
-Let's go, Michael!
-Oh God!

549
00:25:20,060 --> 00:25:22,354
[Kitty exclaims, giggles]

550
00:25:22,437 --> 00:25:23,271
[chuckles]

551
00:25:26,691 --> 00:25:28,693
‎那我们就好好利用吧
Well, let's just make the best of it.

552
00:25:28,777 --> 00:25:30,278
‎我要去趟市场
I am heading to the market

553
00:25:30,362 --> 00:25:34,783
‎买点“菲乐多” “立体脆” “多力多滋”
‎那些零食全都要
'cause I'm going to get Fritos,
Tostitos, Doritos. All the "itos."

554
00:25:34,866 --> 00:25:36,493
‎我卷土重来了 宝贝
I am back, baby!

555
00:25:42,666 --> 00:25:44,251
‎混蛋
Son of a bitch.

556
00:25:44,334 --> 00:25:47,754
[rock music playing]

557
00:25:47,837 --> 00:25:51,550
‎好了 孩子们 地下室归你们了
Okay, kids, the basement is all yours.

558
00:25:51,633 --> 00:25:54,344
‎开着灯 穿着衣服 不许跳舞
Lights on, shirts on, and no dancing.

559
00:25:54,427 --> 00:25:55,512
[Leia laughs]

560
00:25:55,595 --> 00:25:58,139
‎不许跳舞
‎你们像是在演《浑身是劲》
No dancing.
You're like the guy from <i>Footloose.</i>

561
00:26:00,433 --> 00:26:01,476
‎伙计们 不许跳舞
No dancing, you guys.

562
00:26:02,644 --> 00:26:06,481
‎亲爱的 这里放得下三间你家地下室
Babe, you can fit three of your basements
in this basement.

563
00:26:07,399 --> 00:26:09,526
‎听着就费力 妮可
That sounds like a lot of work, Nik.

564
00:26:09,609 --> 00:26:11,319
‎我们就用这个地下室吧
Let's just use <i>this </i>basement.

565
00:26:13,196 --> 00:26:15,073
‎这些旧家具多棒啊？
Don't you love all this old furniture?

566
00:26:15,156 --> 00:26:18,577
‎是的 来几个抱枕
‎再把破伤风针打了就圆满了
Yeah, all we need are some throw pillows
and a tetanus shot.

567
00:26:19,077 --> 00:26:22,956
‎福尔曼夫人 您家真温馨好客
Mrs. Forman, your home is so warm
and inviting.

568
00:26:23,039 --> 00:26:26,710
‎我很期待在这里过暑假
I mean, I can't wait to spend
all summer inside of it. [chuckles]

569
00:26:28,253 --> 00:26:29,921
‎你什么毛病？
What is wrong with you?

570
00:26:32,340 --> 00:26:33,592
‎总之…好了
Anyway… Okay.

571
00:26:33,675 --> 00:26:39,681
‎如果你们觉得无聊
‎我找到些你爸的旧唱片和游戏
Now, if you kids get bored, I found
some old records and games of your dad's,

572
00:26:39,764 --> 00:26:43,018
‎还有一些他不愿让我发现的杂志
and a few magazines
that I don't think he wanted me to see,

573
00:26:43,101 --> 00:26:44,561
‎但我已经扔了
but I got rid of them.

574
00:26:44,644 --> 00:26:45,812
‎她们都是红头发
They were all redheads.

575
00:26:45,895 --> 00:26:47,689
‎他有喜欢的类型
[scoffs] He sure has a type!

576
00:26:48,940 --> 00:26:50,734
‎总之 你们好好玩
Anyhoo, you guys have fun.

577
00:26:54,487 --> 00:26:57,824
‎哇 这东西肯定比任天堂还古早
Whoa, this must be from a Nintendo Zero.

578
00:27:01,202 --> 00:27:02,454
‎不是吧
No way.

579
00:27:03,330 --> 00:27:05,206
‎你奶奶给了我们好东西
Your grandma just hooked us up.

580
00:27:05,790 --> 00:27:07,334
‎-不是吧
‎-必须的
-No way.
-Hell yeah.

581
00:27:07,417 --> 00:27:08,627
‎必须的
Totally.

582
00:27:08,710 --> 00:27:09,628
[laughs]

583
00:27:10,253 --> 00:27:11,087
‎是什么呀？
What is it?

584
00:27:11,796 --> 00:27:14,132
‎最精彩的夏天
Best summer ever!

585
00:27:14,215 --> 00:27:15,550
[all laughing]

586
00:27:15,634 --> 00:27:16,843
‎算我一个
Sign me up!

587
00:27:18,094 --> 00:27:19,596
‎但说真的 是什么呀？
But seriously, what is it?

588
00:27:22,265 --> 00:27:23,391
[rock music playing]

589
00:27:23,475 --> 00:27:24,517
‎一 二 三 四
<i>One, two, three, four!</i>

590
00:27:24,601 --> 00:27:28,813
‎现在是夏天 我们好好开心一下吧
‎咱应该随心所欲做想做的事 对吧？
It's the summer. Let's have fun.
We should do whatever we want. Right?

591
00:27:28,897 --> 00:27:29,981
‎错
Wrong.

592
00:27:30,065 --> 00:27:32,442
‎-你知道我想要什么吗？
‎-别说杰伊
-[Leia] You know what I want?
-Don't say Jay.

593
00:27:32,525 --> 00:27:33,526
‎杰伊
Jay.

594
00:27:34,778 --> 00:27:37,947
‎-你被禁止进入本宅了 出去
‎-不！
-You are banned from this house. Get out.
-No!

595
00:27:38,531 --> 00:27:41,576
‎唐娜 我是凯蒂 你女儿要跟人上床了
Donna, it's Kitty!
Your daughter is about to have sex!

596
00:27:41,660 --> 00:27:42,535
‎她在哪里？
Where is she?

597
00:27:42,619 --> 00:27:45,080
‎等等 所以爸爸
‎并不像他自己说得那么八面玲珑？
Wait, so Dad wasn't as smooth
as he says he was?

598
00:27:45,747 --> 00:27:47,415
‎只能说你的存在是种幸运
Let's just say you're lucky you exist.

599
00:27:47,916 --> 00:27:49,793
‎你们是谁吼了我们家孩子？
Hey, which one of you yelled at my kids?

600
00:27:49,876 --> 00:27:52,170
‎我不知道你的孩子是谁
‎但是他们活该
I don't know which ones are yours,
but they deserved it.

601
00:27:52,253 --> 00:27:54,089
‎他们是格温和内特 另外谢谢
That's Gwen and Nate, and thanks.

602
00:27:54,172 --> 00:27:55,965
‎他在我肚子待了十个月
I was pregnant with him for ten months.

603
00:27:56,049 --> 00:27:58,635
‎医生说没什么问题 但我觉得有问题
The doctor said it was okay,
but I don't think it was.

604
00:27:58,718 --> 00:28:02,263
‎你好像对我的润唇膏过敏
I think you might be having
a reaction to one of my Lip Smackers.

605
00:28:02,764 --> 00:28:03,682
‎真的吗？
Really?

606
00:28:04,599 --> 00:28:08,103
‎-我想向你奶奶出柜
‎-我明天有个面试
-I want to come out to your grandmother.
-I have an interview tomorrow.

607
00:28:08,186 --> 00:28:11,439
‎-你有什么推荐信吗？
‎-我的老板们都很爱我
-[Nikki] Do you have any references?
-Oh, my bosses all loved me.

608
00:28:11,523 --> 00:28:12,482
‎但他们都死了
But they are dead.

609
00:28:12,982 --> 00:28:15,068
[rock music continues]

610
00:28:15,151 --> 00:28:17,237
‎我是同志！
[Ozzie] I'm gaaaay!

611
00:28:17,737 --> 00:28:18,697
‎（菲丝轩）

612
00:28:18,780 --> 00:28:19,948
‎我说 回见您呐
I said, good day.

613
00:28:20,031 --> 00:28:21,533
[all cheering]

614
00:28:22,325 --> 00:28:24,244
[rock music playing]

615
00:29:00,780 --> 00:29:02,282
‎字幕翻译：Zeo Niu

